rified fence, a mircoUSB cable for charging and an integrated hook that can fold for travel. The battery is a 1200 mAh 3.7 V. Full recharge time take 2-6 hours while runtime varies from setting:\nLow - 20 hours\nMid - 8 hours\nHi - 4 hours\nUV - 30 hours\n\nWith all of these fantastic features, it is without a doubt that it will be a must-have in your outdoor, camping, bug out, or garden needs.</p>\n\n\n\t\t\t  <h3>Product Details</h3>\n\t\t\t  <!-- ADD A NEW ROW FOR EACH PRODUCT ATTRIBUTE YOU WANT TO SHOW IN THE TABLE OR YOU CAN REMOVE THE TABLE COMPLETELY-->\n\t\t\t  <div class=\"product-specs\">\n\t\t\t\t  <table>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tbody>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">MPN:</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">SON</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">UPC:</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">706569093247</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">2-IN-1 ZAPPER LAMP - This camping lantern packs a punch with its 600 volt grid electrified fence which is great for fending off bugs, mosquitoes, or insects around your tent or camp area</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">LONG LASTING BATTERY LIFE - The 1200mAh rechargeable battery allows long run times that vary based on its settings: Low - 20 hours, Mid - 8 hours, Hi - 4 hours, and UV - 30 hours and comes with a micro USB cable for quick and universal charging</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">WEATHERPROOF & ADVENTURE READY - Made for the outdoors, this light is rain proof and durable enough to handle the rugged conditions that you love to explore</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">TAKE ANYWHERE - Sitting at 5 inches tall and 4 inches wide you can take this compact, light weight, and portable lantern anywhere: camping, hiking, exploring, adventuring, or traveling abroad</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">SAFE & EASY TO USE - Zapper coil is caged in plastic to prevent unwanted zapping and comes with a hook for convenient hanging in campground or tent</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t  </table>\n\t\t\t  </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t  </div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t  <div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t  <p>&copy; 2024</p>\n\t\t  </div> <!-- /footer -->\n\n\t      </div> <!-- /container -->\n              <div style=\"clear:both\">\n              <table>&nbsp;</table>\n              </div>\n  </body>\n</html> <center><a href=\"https://pages.ebay.com/seller-center/listing/listing-advanced-sellers/third-party-listing-tools.html#third-party-listing-tools\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=0 width=88 height=33 src=\"https://secureimages.channeladvisor.com/images/channeladvisor/channeladvisor_poweredby-en.gif\"></a></center>",
